						<summary>

						<p>Hero-stone (No. 4) set up in a field to the west of the village.</p>						

						<p>Circa 10th century.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record seems to refer to the capture of 300 bulls by a certain <hi rend="italic">[kānpu]</hi> of the Baḷañjigas of Maṅgala.</p>						

